rphous"],"flavor":[{"version":"red","text":"Because of its ability to slip through block walls, it is said to be from an\u00ad other dimension."},{"version":"blue","text":"Because of its ability to slip through block walls, it is said to be from an\u00ad other dimension."},{"version":"yellow","text":"By licking, it saps the victim's life. It causes shaking that won't stop until the victim's demise."},{"version":"gold","text":"In total darkness, where nothing is visible, HAUNTER lurks, silently stalking its next victim."},{"version":"silver","text":"Its tongue is made of gas. If licked, its victim starts shaking constantly until death even\u00ad tually comes."},{"version":"crystal","text":"It hides in the dark, planning to take the life of the next living thing that wanders close by."},{"version":"ruby","text":"HAUNTER is a dangerous POK\u00e9MON. If one beckons you while floating in darkness, you must never approach it. This POK\u00e9MON will try to lick you with its tongue and steal your life away."},{"version":"sapphire","text":"HAUNTER is a dangerous POK\u00e9MON. If one beckons you while floating in darkness, you must never approach it. This POK\u00e9MON will try to lick you with its tongue and steal your life away."},{"version":"emerald","text":"If a HAUNTER beckons you while it is floating in darkness, don\u2019t approach it. This POK\u00e9MON will try to lick you with its tongue and steal your life away."},{"version":"firered","text":"If you get the feeling of being watched in darkness when nobody is around, HAUNTER is there."},{"version":"leafgreen","text":"Because of its ability to slip through block walls, it is said to be from another dimension."},{"version":"diamond","text":"It can slip through any obstacle. It lurks inside walls to keep an eye on its foes."},{"version":"pearl","text":"It licks with its gaseous tongue to steal the victim\u2019s life force. It lurks in darkness for prey."},{"version":"platinum","text":"It likes to lurk in the dark and tap shoulders with a gaseous hand. Its touch causes endless shuddering."},{"version":"heartgold","text":"In total darkness, where nothing is visible, HAUNTER lurks, silently stalking its next victim."},{"version":"soulsilver","text":"Its tongue is made of gas. If licked, its victim starts shaking constantly until death eventually comes."},{"version":"black","text":"It likes to lurk in the dark and tap shoulders with a gaseous hand. Its touch causes endless shuddering."},{"version":"white","text":"It likes to lurk in the dark and tap shoulders with a gaseous hand. Its touch causes endless shuddering."},{"version":"black-2","text":"It likes to lurk in the dark and tap shoulders with a gaseous hand. Its touch causes endless shuddering."},{"version":"white-2","text":"It likes to lurk in the dark and tap shoulders with a gaseous hand. Its touch causes endless shuddering."},{"version":"x","text":"If you get the feeling of being watched in darkness when nobody is around, Haunter is there."},{"version":"y","text":"It licks with its gaseous tongue to steal the victim\u2019s life force. It lurks in darkness for prey."},{"version":"omega-ruby","text":"Haunter is a dangerous Pok\u00e9mon. If one beckons you while floating in darkness, you must never approach it. This Pok\u00e9mon will try to lick you with its tongue and steal your life away."},{"version":"alpha-sapphire","text":"Haunter is a dangerous Pok\u00e9mon. If one beckons you while floating in darkness, you must never approach it. This Pok\u00e9mon will try to lick you with its tongue and steal your life away."},{"version":"sun","text":"It strikes at humans from total darkness. Those licked by its cold tongue grow weaker with each passing day until they die."},{"version":"moon","text":"It fears the light and revels in the dark. It may be on the verge of extinction in cities that stay brightly lit at night."},{"version":"ultra-sun","text":"On moonless nights, Haunter searches for someone to curse, so it\u2019s best not to go out walking around."},{"version":"ultra-moon","text":"It\u2019s dangerous to go outside alone on nights when you\u2019re feeling sad. Haunter will catch you, and you won\u2019t be able to go back home."},{"version":"lets-go-pikachu","text":"By licking, it saps the victim\u2019s life. It causes shaking that won\u2019t stop until the victim\u2019s demise."},{"version":"lets-go-eevee","text":"By licking, it saps the victim\u2019s life. It causes shaking that won\u2019t stop until the victim\u2019s demise."},{"version":"sword","text":"Its tongue is made of gas. If licked, its victim starts shaking constantly until death eventually comes."},{"version":"shield","text":"If you get the feeling of being watched in darkness when nobody is around, Haunter is there."},{"version":"legends-arceus","text":"This frightful, malevolent spirit can glide through walls, appearing wherever it likes. According to rumor, victims of a Haunter's lick will wither to death day by day."}],"evo":{"name":"gastly","level":0,"min_level":null,"trigger":null,"item":null,"held_item":null,"known_move":null,"known_move_type":null,"location":null,"min_affection":null,"min_beauty":null,"min_happiness":null,"needs_overworld_rain":false,"time_of_day":null,"turn_upside_down":false,"evolves_to":[{"name":"haunter","level":1,"min_level":25,"trigger":"level-up","item":null,"held_item":null,"known_move":null,"known_move_type":null,"location":null,"min_affection":null,"min_beauty":null,"min_happiness":null,"needs_overworld_rain":false,"time_of_day":"","turn_upside_down":false,"evolves_to":[{"name":"gengar","level":2,"min_level":null,"trigger":"trade","item":null,"held_item":null,"known_move":null,"known_move_type":null,"location":null,"min_affection":null,"min_beauty":null,"min_happiness":null,"needs_overworld_rain":false,"time_of_day":"","turn_upside_down":false,"evolves_to":[]}]}]},"sprite":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/93.png","shiny":"https://raw.githubusercontent.